Peter Jones "cike da haushi" bayan Holly Willoughby ya janye daga yarjejeniyarsa da aka yi da shi na fam miliyan 11
An bar tauraron 'Dragons' Den Peter Jones a "cikin fushi" bayan mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin Holly Willoughby ya janye daga yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11 da salon rayuwarsa don mai da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarsa da Marks da Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba shi da lokacin yin amfani da kayan gida da kayan haɗi na Truly.
An kwatanta wannan kamfani da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop.
Mai gabatar da shirin, mai shekara 37, ta wallafa a shafinta na Instagram cewa ta bar aikin.
Holly Willoughby ta bar tauraron 'Dan wasan Dragons Peter Jones cikin fushi bayan ta janye daga kasuwancin rayuwarsu mai riba a minti na karshe  don mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarta da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Majiyoyi sun ce Jones ta yi "haushi" lokacin da shahararriyar 'yar talbijin ta bayyana a wani taro mai cike da tashin hankali a ranar Talata a hedkwatar daular kasuwancinsa da ke Marlow a Buckinghamshire cewa sabbin yarjejeniyoyinta  da suka kai darajar fam miliyan 1.5  na nufin ba ta da isasshen lokaci don kayan gida da kayan haɗi na Truly.
An kwatanta kamfanin da Gwyneth Paltrow Goop kuma an yi la'akari da shi don ninka darajar Willoughby na GBP 11 miliyan.
Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ta shiga shafinta na Instagram don sanar da cewa ta bar Truly, yayin da Jones ke tashi daga Burtaniya zuwa wani gidan hutu.
Wani majiya ya ce: "Truly yana cikin abubuwan da Holly take so.
Wannan aikin da za ta yi zai ɗauki shekaru da yawa.
Wannan shawarar da ta yanke ta ba kowa mamaki.
Babu wanda zai yarda da abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, kusan lokacin da aka kaddamar da shi.
"Akwai kaya da yawa a cikin ofishin Marlow da aka shirya don sayarwa".
Masana sun ce, barin wannan jaridar da ke cikin jaridun da suke samun kuɗi sosai a ƙasar Britaniya zai iya jawo wa kamfanin hasara sosai domin yawan kuɗin da aka kashe a kan kayayyaki  daga matashin kai zuwa kyandir da tufafi da kayayyakin gida  da kuma yiwuwar ƙarin jinkiri.
Kuma hakan zai iya kawo ƙarshen abokantaka mai tsawo.
Mahaifiyar yara uku Willoughby da maigidan Dan Baldwin sun kasance suna da dangantaka mai kyau da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp tsawon shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a shekara ta 2016, kuma Jones, 52, ya zama shugaban kwamitin a watan Maris.
Ma'aurata biyu suna hutu tare, kuma Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin dari na hannun jari a kamfanin samar da talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby zai zama jakadan M&S kuma zai maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin ITV na I'm A Celebrity.
Wata majiya da ke kusa da Jones ta ce a daren jiya, "ba za mu iya yin tsokaci kan harkokin kasuwancinsa ba".
