Taron zaben Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron masu kada kuri'a a wannan karon a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shine taron farko na Trump na biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tarurruka a wurare masu son Trump kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da aka dakatar da zaben tabbatar da alƙalin da Trump ya nada a kan kujerar Kotun Koli, Trump yana ƙoƙarin samun goyon baya don zaɓen tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican suna fuskantar haɗarin rasa iko a kan Majalisar Dokoki lokacin da aka jefa kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron zaɓen Trump a yammacin Virginia kuma ta yaya za ka iya kallon shi a kan layi?
Za a gudanar da taron zaben Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a tsakar dare tsakanin ranar Asabar, 29 ga Nuwamba, da Lahadi, 30 ga Nuwamba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron zaben Trump a West Virginia ta yanar gizo ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana ne game da sauraron shari'ar da za a yi a wannan makon game da Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli, wanda ya yi tashin hankali saboda zargin cin zarafin mata, kuma an dakatar da kuri'ar da ake tsammani a majalisar dattijai game da tabbatarwa har tsawon mako guda yayin da FBI ke binciken tuhumar.
Amma babban burin wannan taron zaɓe shi ne samar da ƙarfin hali ga 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar babban zaɓen watan Nuwamba.
Mutanen da ke kan yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump sun ce taron masu zabe guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, na nufin "samar da kuzari tsakanin masu sa kai da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma kara yawan rinjaye da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandarsa, shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya, yanzu da muka shiga lokacin kamfen", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ba a bayyana sunansa ba, ya shaida wa Reuters.
An gudanar da taron zaben na daren yau a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling kuma ana sa ran jan hankalin magoya bayan Trump daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a ba da rahoto daga Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne dai Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya bukaci ya fito don ya ba shi goyon baya a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, wanda ke nazarin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
