Turai na da babbar dama a wasan karshe na gasar Ryder Cup bayan da ta fito daga wasan hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar, inda ta fi Amurka 10-6.
Kyakkyawan wasan kwaikwayo Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci hanya tare da nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods mai wahala kuma ya zuwa yanzu ya sami maki hudu a Le Golf National.
