Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones Kit Harington yana neman wani abu mai guba.
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda yin amfani da takobi a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin HBO mai ban tsoro na wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones.
Amma, ɗan wasan mai shekara 31 ya yi watsi da ra'ayin nan cewa maza ne jarumawa kuma ya ce irin waɗannan halayen suna sa matasa maza su ji cewa dole ne su yi tsauri don a daraja su.
Kit ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times Culture cewa yana ganin "wani abu ya faru" kuma ya tambayi yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa a cikin zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda ya yi aure kwanan nan da Rose Leslie, 'yar wasan kwaikwayo ta Game of Thrones, a shekara ta 31, ya ce matsalar ta "ɗau hankalinsa sosai".
"A kwanakin nan, ina yawan tunani game da abin da ya faru da maza a birnin", in ji shi.
"Idan muka dubi matsalolin da muke fuskanta a yau, menene muka koya wa samari a lokacin da suke girma?"
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na abin da ya sa ake ƙara yawan maza masu haɗari saboda halayen maza.
Ya ci gaba: "Abin da aka haifa, da abin da aka koya?
Menene matasa maza suke koya daga talabijin da kuma tituna da ke sa su ji cewa su maza ne?
Ina ganin wannan ita ce babbar tambaya a zamaninmu, ta yaya za mu canza wannan?
Gama a bayyane yake cewa wani abu ya faru da waɗannan matasa".
A lokacin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani abu ba game da Game of Thrones lokacin da jerin suka ƙare a bazara mai zuwa, yana cewa ya "ƙare da filayen yaƙi da dawakai".
Kit za ta fito a watan Nuwamba a sake yin fim din Sam Shepard na True West, wanda ke ba da labarin wani mai shirya fim da kuma ɗan'uwansa da ya yi fashi.
Actor din ya bayyana kwanan nan cewa ya dauki haduwa da matarsa Rose a matsayin mafi kyawu a cikin dukkanin kwarewar wasan kwaikwayo.
"Na sadu da matata saboda wannan jerin, don haka ta wannan hanyar ta ba ni iyalina na gaba kuma ta tsara rayuwata har abada", in ji shi.
Rose ta buga Ygritte, wanda Jon Snow, ɗan wasan kwaikwayo na Kit, ya ƙaunace shi, a cikin jerin fina-finai na Emmy.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yunin 2018 a gidan Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta Bayyana Ƙaruwar Sabbin Cutar Nan da Kashi 14
Kasar Sin ta bayyana karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar kanjamau.
Hukumar kiwon lafiya ta ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a ƙasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin mutane 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar.
Mafi yawan sabbin cututtukan sun kamu ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda sabon abu ne.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa da sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar karban jini daga mutane da cutar ta shafa.
Amma, an rage adadin mutane da suke kamuwa da cutar zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na ƙasar Sin a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Amma a cikin shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Kwayar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
A shekara ta 1997, an halatta luwadi, amma ana nuna bambanci ga mutanen da suke yin jima'i da ke nuna bambanci da ke tsakanin maza da mata.
Bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke kwana da maza suna auren mata domin al'adarsu ta nuna cewa suna son mutane su bi ƙa'idodin addini.
Yawancin cututtukan cututtuka suna faruwa ne saboda rashin amfani da maganin hana haihuwa a waɗannan yanayi.
Tun a shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar samun magani kyauta da daidaito don magance cutar HIV.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa ma'aikatanta sun fallasa bayanan Sanatocin Republican, kuma tana mai tsaurara murya kan "ƙarya mai haɗari" da kuma "ra'ayoyin maƙarƙashiya"
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisar wakilai Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin da ake yi mata cewa wani a cikin ma'aikatanta ya raba bayanan sirri na sanatoci uku na Republican a shafukan Wikipedia.
Wani dan Democrat daga Los Angeles ya yi ikirarin cewa zargin ya fito ne daga shafukan yanar gizo da kuma goyon bayan "mafi girma dama".
Waters ya rubuta a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "Maƙaryaci, ƙarya da kuma ƙarin munanan ƙaryace-ƙaryace".
Bayanan da aka wallafa sun ƙunshi adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na Sanata Lindsey Graham na jihar South Carolina da kuma Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, waɗanda duka daga Utah ne.
Wani mutum da ba a san ko wane ne ba ya wallafa wannan bayanin a shafin yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis a kan fadar shugaban kasa a lokacin da ake sauraron karar da majalisar dattawa ta yi kan zargin cin zarafin dan majalisar dattijai Brett Kavanaugh.
Bayan da Sanatoci uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi ne aka yi wannan fashin.
Shafukan yada labarai na masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar Gateway Pundit na RedState sun bayyana cewa adiresoshin IP sun nuna cewa mutanen Waters ne suka sanya bayanan, sannan suka wallafa bayanan wani ma'aikacin Waters, in ji The Hill.
"Wannan tuhuma ba ta da tushe kuma ƙarya ce", in ji Waters.
"Memba na wanda ke cikin ma'aikatata wanda ke da mutuncinsa, bayanansa da amincinsa sun lalace sakamakon wadannan zarge-zarge na karya, ba shi da wani alhakin wannan bayanan da aka bata.
Wannan tuhuma ba ta da tushe kuma ƙarya ce kwarai da gaske".
Waters ta bayyana cewa, ta yi saurin fuskantar suka a shafukan yanar gizo, ciki har da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda ne mai tsanani", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ta da halin da ya dace da zama 'yar majalisa.
Idan aka zarge ka da abin da ba ka yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Kada ka yi rashin biyayya.
Ba za a iya tambayar dalilan da ke sa ake tuhumar ba.
Ka kasance da kwanciyar hankali".
Fleischer ya kwatanta yadda Waters ya amsa da yadda 'yan Democrat suka soki Kavanaugh, wanda aka zargi da yin fushi a lokacin sauraron shari'ar ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican da ke neman maye gurbin Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, ya kuma bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Babban, idan gaskiya ne", in ji shi.
A cikin sanarwar da Waters ta fitar, ta ce ma'aikatanta sun tuntubi "mahukuntan da suka dace da kuma hukumomin tsaro game da wadannan maganganun na yaudara".
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano wadanda suka aikata wannan laifin", in ji ta, "kuma za a hukunta su bisa hukunce-hukuncen da suka aikata, wanda ke da lahani da kuma hadari ga kowa da kowa a cikin ma'aikatata".
