Mene ne bikin 'yan ƙasa na duniya, kuma shin ya taimaka wajen rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizens Festival  wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara da ke nuna masu fasaha masu ban sha'awa da kuma wata manufa mai ban sha'awa; don kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
A karo na bakwai, bikin na Global Citizens Festival zai karbi dubban mutane a manyan filayen Central Park don kallon kide kide da Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes, yayin da bikin ke kara wayar da kan jama'a kan ainihin burin da ake da shi na kawo karshen talauci a shekarar 2030.
An fara bikin na Global Citizen a shekarar 2012 kuma wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta ta kasa da kasa da ke yaki da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan masu adawa da ita.
Don a samu tikitin zuwa taron kyauta (idan ba za ka biya kuɗin tikitin VIP ba), ana bukatar masu halartar su yi ayyuka ko kuma "ayyuka" da yawa, kamar yin aikin sa kai, rubuta wa wani shugaban duniya wasiƙa, yin waya, ko kuma wani abu mai ma'ana da zai sa a san cewa an kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar Global Citizen ta kasance, yanzu da suka rage shekaru 12 don cimma burin?
Shin kyautar kyauta ta kyauta ta kawo canji na gaske, ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "clicktivism" , wato mutane suna jin cewa suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takardun shiga yanar gizo ko kuma yin tweet?
Global Citizen ta ce tun daga shekara ta 2011, ta samu fiye da "aiki" miliyan 19 daga 'yanta.
Sun ce wadannan ayyuka sun sa shugabannin duniya su sanya manufofi da manufofi masu mahimmanci da kuma manufofi masu mahimmanci, wanda ya kai dala biliyan 37, wanda a shekara ta 2030 ana sa ran zai shafi mutane fiye da biliyan 2.25.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta lissafa manufofi da ayyuka 390 da suka samu sakamakon ayyukansu, wanda ya kai sama da dala biliyan 10 da aka riga aka biya ko aka tara.
Ƙungiyar ta ce waɗannan kayayyakin sun shafi mutane kusan miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Daya daga cikin manyan manufofin shi ne The Power of Nutrition, wanda aka fara a Ingila, haɗin gwiwar masu saka jari da masu aiki da yaƙi, wanda ke da niyyar "taimaka wa yara su cika damar su" kuma ya yi alkawarin dala miliyan 35 don magance matsalar abinci mai gina jiki a Rwanda bayan karɓar tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Ingila, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin wasu ƙasashe da kuma 'yan ƙasa kamar ku, rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki zai iya zama alamar tarihi", in ji jakadan The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, ga masu sauraro a wani wasan kwaikwayo a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce gwamnatin Ingila ta yi alkawarin samar da kudade don inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga uwaye da yara bayan karbar kira sama da 5,000 a yanar gizo.
A amsa ga wata tambaya da ake yawan yi a shafin, "Me ya sa ka gaskata cewa za mu iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
Global Citizen ta rubuta: "Za a yi gwagwarmaya mai tsawo da wuya, kuma a wasu lokatai za mu yi tuntuɓe kuma mu yi kuskure.
Amma kamar yadda yake da 'yancin jama'a da kuma 'yan adawa da wariyar launin fata, zai yi nasara domin muna da ƙarfi".
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B da Janelle Monáe na cikin masu halartar bikin na wannan shekara a birnin New York.
Amurka na iya amfani da sojan ruwanta don "toshe" kayayyakin da Rasha ke fitarwa na makamashi, in ji sakataren harkokin cikin gida na Amurka
"Idan ya cancanta", Washington na iya amfani da sojan ruwanta don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwa, gami da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke, ga Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya yi iƙirarin cewa sa hannun Rasha a Syria  musamman inda suke aiki a gayyatar da gwamnatin da ta dace  hujja ce ta faɗaɗa sayar da makamashin su.
Ya ce: "Ina ganin suna Gabas ta Tsakiya ne domin suna son sayar da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabas da Kudancin Turai".
Kuma a cewarsa akwai hanyoyi da kuma albarkatun da za su hana hakan.
"Amurka tana da damar da ke cikin jiragen ruwanta na tabbatar da cewa akwai 'yanci a hanyoyin teku, kuma idan ya zama dole, za mu iya toshe su don tabbatar da cewa makamashi ba ya shiga kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ga masu sauraro a taron da Ƙungiyar Ƙarfin Makamashi ta Masu Amfani  ta shirya, wata ƙungiya mai zaman kanta da ke ɗaukan kanta a matsayin "muryar masu amfani da makamashi na Amirka" .
Ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke hulda da Rasha da Iran, ya ce sun yi kama.
"Dole ne a yi amfani da man fetur a matsayin wata hanya ta samun ci gaba a tattalin arziki", in ji shi, inda ya kira Rasha da "farar fata mai amfani da man fetur" wanda tattalin arzikinta ya dogara da burbushin mai.
Wannan magana ta biyo bayan gwamnatin Trump da ke son kara yawan kayayyakin da Turai ke fitarwa na gas wanda zai maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ita ce mafi arha ga masu amfani da ita a Turai.
Don cimma wannan, masu magana da yawun gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da Donald Trump da kansa, sun yi kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin layin Nord Stream 2 wanda ba daidai ba, wanda a cewar Trump ya mayar da Berlin "kurkuku" na Moscow.
Moscow ta sha nanata cewa aikin Nord Stream 2 mai tsadar biliyan 11 da ake sa ran zai ninka karfinsa zuwa biliyan 110 na murabba'in mita, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya ce Washington ta nuna rashin amincewa da wannan shiri ne saboda rashin daidaiton yanayi kuma saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki.
"Ina ganin mun yarda cewa ba za a yi amfani da makamashi a matsayin kayan aiki ba, kuma masu amfani da makamashi su sami damar zaɓar mai samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha, Alexander Novak, a wani taron da ya biyo baya a Moscow tare da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka, Rick Perry, a watan Satumba.
Matsayin Amurkawa ya gamu da suka daga Jamus, wadda ta tabbatar da cewa za ta shiga cikin aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, BDI, ta bukaci Amurka da ta kauce wa tsoma baki a cikin manufofin samar da makamashi na EU da yarjejeniyar kasashen biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala da wani ɓangare na uku ya tsoma baki a cikin samar da makamashi", in ji shugaban BDI, Dieter Kempf, bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren "tana tunanin sosai" ta tsaya takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020, in ji Sanatan Massachusetts
Sanata daga Massachusetts Elizabeth Warren "tana tunanin sosai" ta tsaya takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara, in ji ta a ranar Asabar.
A wani taron majalisar dattawa a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa tana tunanin yin takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara tsarin siyasarmu, kuma hakan na bukatar mace a gaba", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ya bayyana ra'ayinsa game da Shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin taron majalisar gari, yana cewa yana "kaiwa kasar nan ta hanyar da ba ta dace ba".
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ya kasance mai tsananin sukar Trump da kuma dan majalisar dattijai Brett Kavanaugh.
A wani sakon Twitter a ranar Juma'a, Warren ya rubuta cewa, "Tabbas, FBI za ta binciki lamarin kafin a kada kuri'a".
Amma, binciken da aka yi a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin mutanen garin Warren ba su yarda da cewa za ta yi takara a shekarar 2020 ba.
A cewar wani binciken da aka yi daga Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk da kuma Boston Globe, kashi 58 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata Sanatan ya yi takara ba.
32 cikin dari sun goyi bayan yiwuwar takara.
Binciken ya nuna goyon baya ga tsohon gwamna Deval Patrick da kashi 38 cikin dari da kashi 48 cikin dari na yiwuwar.
Sauran manyan 'yan takarar jam'iyyar Democrat da ake tattaunawa a zaben shugaban kasa na shekarar 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai sanar da hukuncinsa a watan Janairu.
Sarah Palin ta ambaci Track Palin a taron zaben Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki bayan ya shiga soja a watan Satumba.
A ranar Litinin da yamma aka kama shi kuma aka tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin mata a gida.
"Abin da ɗana ya shiga bayan ya dawo gida ya sa na iya danganta da sauran iyalai waɗanda ke jin tasirin PTSD da sauran raunin da sojojinmu ke dawowa da su", in ji ta ga jama'a a taron masu jefa ƙuri'ar Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira kama shi "giwa a sararin samaniya" kuma ta ce game da ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojoji "sun canza kuma sun zama masu tsauri.
An kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin wata mata a gida, hana yin rahoton cin zarafin a gida da kuma mallakar makami a cikin maye, in ji Dan Bennet, mai magana da yawun 'yan sanda a Wasillas.
Jihohi 18 da D.C. sun goyi bayan adawa da sabuwar dokar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan ƙin amincewa da sabuwar dokar Amurka da ke hana masu fama da tashin hankali daga gidajensu da kuma ƙungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda mafaka.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da D.C. sun gabatar da wata sanarwa a Washington a ranar Juma'a, a madadin wani mai neman mafaka da ke adawa da dokar, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace da Sessions ba, wadda kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta, game da dokar tarayya.
Ta ce abokin aikinta "da 'ya'yansa maza masu cin zarafi, 'yan kungiyar' sun yi mata fyaɗe, amma jami'an Amurka sun ƙi ta neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas.
Masu gabatar da kara da ke goyon bayan Grace sun kwatanta El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, inda yawancin masu neman mafaka daga Amurka suka fito, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fama da matsalolin ƙungiyoyi da kuma tashin hankali a gida.
Sabuwar dokar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta yi watsi da shawarar da Hukumar Kula da 'Yan Gudun Hijira ta Amurka ta yanke a shekarar 2014 wanda ya ba da damar baƙi marasa izini da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida su nemi mafaka.
A ranar Jumma'a, Karl Racine, lauyan ofishin lauya na D.C., ya ce sabuwar dokar "ta yi watsi da dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na duniya da aka kafa shekaru da yawa".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a yanke hukunci kan duk wani bukatar neman mafaka bisa ga hujjoji da kuma yanayi da ya dace, kuma irin wannan shinge ya sabawa wannan ka'ida", in ji sanarwar da jam'iyyar ta fitar.
Lauyoyin sun kuma yi jayayya a cikin sanarwar cewa dokar da ta ƙi baƙi tana cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka saboda sun fi dacewa su zama masu zaman kansu kuma "suna samar da ma'aikata masu mahimmanci".
A watan Yuni, alkalin shari'a Jeff Sessions ya hana alƙalai na shige da fice izinin ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na gida da na ƙungiya.
"Ana ba da mafaka ga waɗanda suka bar ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoro saboda launin fata, addini, ƙasa ko membobin wata ƙungiya ko siyasa", in ji Sessions a cikin sanarwar da ya bayar a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa nufin cewa mafaka za ta magance dukan matsaloli  ko kuma matsaloli masu tsanani  da mutane suke fuskanta a ko'ina cikin duniya a kowace rana ba.
Yayin da adadin mutanen da suka mutu ya ninka, sai aka soma kokarin gano wadanda suka tsira a Palu.
Amma, waɗanda suka tsira sun ƙara yin baƙin ciki.
"Yana da wuya sosai", in ji Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiya 'yar shekara 35, yayin da take ta'azantar da ɗanta da ke fama da zazzabi a wani cibiyar ceto a birnin Palu da aka halaka.
"Kowace minti, ana kawo gawarwakin mutane a cikin motar asibiti.
