Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da amfani da hanyoyin da ba su dace ba da kuma tallata tallace-tallace
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke bayyana amfanin hadin gwiwar Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba game da buga jaridar China Daily a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register  jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa  bayan da ya zargi China da tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattijai na ranar 6 ga Nuwamba.
Jami'an Amurka sun shaida wa Reuters cewa zargin Trump na tsoma baki da China ta yi a zaben Amurka ya nuna wani sabon mataki a yakin da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan China.
Ko da yake al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su yi tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, yanzu Beijing da Washington sun shiga cikin yakin cinikayya mai tsanani, inda suka yi ta saka haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
Kudaden da kasar Sin ta saka a yakin cinikayya, za su shafi masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican, in ji masana kasar Sin da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China tsohon gwamnan Iowa na tsawon shekaru, wanda babban mai fitar da kayan abinci ne ga kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wata edita a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi cewa China tana "ƙara amfani da munanan hanyoyin ta hanyar tallata tallace-tallace a cikin 'yan jaridarmu".
"Ta hanyar yada farfaganda, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da' yancin manema labarai ta hanyar buga wani talla a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A cikin gidajen talla a nan Beijing, za ka ga 'yan ra'ayoyi ne kawai, kuma ba za ka samu cikakken bayanin ra'ayoyin jama'ar kasar Sin game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar ba, saboda kafofin yada labarai suna karkashin tsananin kulawar jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa "wani daga cikin manyan jaridun kasar Sin ya ki buga" labarinsa, ko da yake bai ce wane ba.
'Yan Republican na nuna wa mata wariya a gaban zaben tsakiyar shekara, masu sharhi sun yi gargadin cewa, batun Kavanaugh ya janyo tashin hankali.
Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican ke goyon bayan dan takarar kotun kolin kasar Brett Kavanaugh kan zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za su fuskanci mummunan tashin hankali a zaben da ke tafe, musamman daga mata.
Wannan lamari ya jawo tashin hankali a tsakanin 'yan Republican da dama, kuma sun bayyana cewa suna son ci gaba da zaben.
"Ba za a iya sake yin wannan ba", in ji Grant Reher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell na Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da ta wallafa a The Hill a ranar Asabar.
Reher ya ce yana shakkar cewa bukatar Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona na neman binciken FBI a cikin awa 11 zai rage fushin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba  ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma kakakin kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn, a cewar The Hill a ranar Juma'a.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zanga a wani zanga-zanga a majalisar dattawa sun yi ihu "Nuwamba tana zuwa!" lokacin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka zabi su ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Farfesa Christine Blasey Ford, in ji Mic.
"Jami'ar demokradiyya da kuma kwarin gwiwarta za su kai sabon matsayi", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa.
"Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya kai matsayi mai girma; gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya kaiwa mafi girma, musamman ma tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a cikin unguwannin karkara da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a  masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29  waɗanda ba sa yawan jefa kuri'a, duk da rashin son shugaban kasa".
Tun kafin Ford ya yi zargin cin zarafin dan takarar kotun kolin, manazarta sun ce idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da neman takarar, hakan zai haifar da koma baya.
"Ya zama mafi muni ga 'yan Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun zaben kwamitin ba ne ko sakamakon karshe ko kuma ko za a tuhumi Kavanaugh; amma kuma batun yadda 'yan Republican suka yi da ita da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, shugaban kungiyar 'Priorities USA'  wata kungiya da ke goyon bayan 'yan Democrat a zaben .
Amma jama'ar Amirka sun nuna ra'ayi daban-daban game da wanda za su gaskata bayan shaidun Ford da Kavanaugh, wanda ya fi yawa.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na masu amsa sun gaskata ko kuma sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin dari suka ce sun gaskata ko kuma sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun yi imani cewa Kavanaugh ko dai mai yiwuwa ne ko kuma tabbas ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce haka game da Ford.
Bayan kiran Flake, FBI yanzu tana binciken zargin da Ford da akalla wani ya yi, in ji Deborah Ramirez na The Guardian.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade lokacin da take da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ta ce, wanda aka zaba a matsayin mai neman shugaban kasa ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a wani biki a lokacin da suke Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro intanet yana shirin kirkirar sabuwar intanet da zata fafata da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro intanet, ya kaddamar da wani sabon kamfani da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da kamfanin fasaha ya yi shi ne Inrupt, wani kamfani ne da ke amfani da dandamali mai buɗewa na Berners-Lee mai suna Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar abin da ke ciki.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners Lee ya yi dariya cewa shirin Inrupt "mulkin duniya" ne.
"Dole ne mu yi hakan yanzu", in ji shi game da kasuwancin da aka fara.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Wannan app ɗin yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu "taro na sirri na kan layi" ko POD.
Zai iya ƙunsar jerin sunayen abokan hulɗa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalandarku, ɗakunan karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna cikin burauzar guda a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da banbanci game da tattara bayanan sirri na kan layi shine cewa yana da cikakken damar mai amfani don yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun damar wannan takamaiman bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafawa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar shugaban kamfanin, John Bruce, shine a tara albarkatu, matakai da iyawa don samar da Solid ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka software a kan kwangilar aiki da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Daga wannan makon masu fasaha a duk duniya za su iya yin nasu aikace-aikacen rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook ko Google game da ko za su canza kome gaba ɗaya don su daina amfani da tsarin kasuwancin su".
"Ba ma neman izininku".
A wani rubutu a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt "na da manufa ta samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai iya tabbatar da mutuncin da ingancin sabuwar intanet da aka gina a kan Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a yanar gizo lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance babbar murya a cikin abin da ake kira muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Yayin da Inrupt ya fara, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa mai kirkiro da kuma darektan Cibiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, Gidauniyar Yanar Gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa game da lokacin da za a yi amfani da intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: An Ba da Godiya ga Limamin da Ya Sami Gwarzon Victoria a Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
An yi bikin cika shekaru 100 da samun limamin cocin Ingila da ya lashe lambar yabo ta Victoria a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya.
Laftanar Colonel kuma Firist Bernard Wann ya lashe lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a lokacin da ake kai hari a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma bayan kwana huɗu, wani ɗan harbi ya kashe shi kuma bai taɓa sanin cewa ya sami lambar yabo mafi girma ta soja ba.
A ranar Asabar, jikokinsa biyu sun bayyana wani abin tunawa a wani biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
