Wannan ba abin farin ciki ba ne".
"Babu wani abu da ya fi muhimmanci game da jima'i".
Mai tsalle-tsalle na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya ji cewa ba shi da daraja a lokacin da yake girma saboda jima'i, amma hakan ya motsa shi ya yi nasara.
Matashin mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci hakan ba kafin ya shiga manyan makarantu cewa "ba kowa ba ne kamar ni".
A lokacin da yake Radio 4's first Desert Island Discs with Lauren Laverne, ya ce yana magana ne game da hakkin 'yan luwadi don ya ba wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce ba ya son lashe gasar Olympics bayan ya zama mahaifi.
