Wannan gwarzon dan wasa mai cin kofin Olympics sau biyu ya zama babban mai fafutukar kare hakkin bil'adama na LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da halartar wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don yin kira ga haramta luwadi a wasu kasashe.
