An yi wa dan wasan Tennessee State Tigers Christion Abercrombie tiyata bayan da ya ji rauni a kan kai a wasan da suka doke Vanderbilt Commodores 31-27 a ranar Asabar, in ji Mike Organ na Tennessee.
Kociyan tawagar Tennessee Rod Reed ya shaida wa manema labarai cewa lamarin ya faru ne kafin a kammala wasan.
