Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a suka kashe, in ji hukumomi, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Da yake hanyoyin sadarwa sun lalace, ma'aikatan agaji ba su iya samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin Palu ba, wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan girgizar ƙasar ta auku.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne kuma yana cikin ƙasan wani ɗan ƙaramin kwari a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi wanda a cikin 2017 ya yi kiyasin yawan jama'a 379,800.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da haihuwar Yesu.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gwamnatin, wanda yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardi, a cikin 2017 yana da yawan jama'a 299.200.
Kifi da noma sune ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin Tsakiyar Slavic, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Nickel mining ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi yana faruwa ne a Morowali, wanda shine gabar tekun da ke gaban Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce, tsunamis sun addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, wata guguwar tsunami ta sake addabar garin Donggala kuma ta kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Rim kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a shekarun baya sun haɗa da:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonesia ta haddasa tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gaɓar tekun Indiya, har da fiye da rabin mutanen da ke Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya haddasa tsunami da ya auku a kudancin tsibirin kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afku a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai da ke bakin tekun Sumatra kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya da ke Aceh, ta haddasa barna da firgici yayin da jama'a ke tunawa da girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane a 2004.
Ko da yake ba a yi tsunami ba a wannan lokacin, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a lokacin da gine-ginen suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na ƙasar Indonesia, ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
