Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun da ke kula da shari'a ta gabatar da Saipov da laifin aikata laifuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan gilla da ake yi a cikin 'yan bindiga, da ake amfani da su a kotun da ke tuhumar masu aikata laifuka, da kuma laifuka daya na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi sosai", kuma sun bayyana hukuncin da Saipov ya yanke a matsayin "mummunan, mugun, da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haddasa raunin jiki da kuma asarar dangi da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da Kotu ta Kudu ta New York ta yi watsi da hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan wasu masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekara ta 1953, an yanke hukuncin kisa a New York don zargin Julius da Ethel Rosenberg da suka yi aikin leƙen asiri a lokacin Cold War.
An kashe Rosenberg da matarsa a kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov dan asalin Uzbekistan ne kuma bisa ga takardun kotu bai nuna alamar nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
A cewar tuhumar, Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa kallon bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa ne ya sa ya kai harin.
Ya kuma nemi a rataye tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa, jami'an sun shaida.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan abubuwa 22 da ake tuhumarsa da su.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin Saipov ya ce "ba shakka mun yi takaici" da hukuncin da masu gabatar da kara suka yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar bin hukuncin kisa da kuma ƙin yarda da furci da kuma ɗaurin rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai ƙara tsawaita rauni ga duk waɗanda ke ciki", in ji Patton.
A baya dai, lauyoyin Saipov sun nemi masu gabatar da kara da su guji yankewa Saipov hukuncin kisa.
Ministan kare hakkin bil adama ya ce ya kamata Nigel FARAGE ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "tallafawa sojojin jama'a" a wani zanga-zanga a majalisa a yau.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa na bukatar su "dauko matsin lamba" daga masu shakkar kudin Euro bayan da wani ministan Theresa May ya ce Farage ya dauki nauyin tattaunawar da EU.
Wani dan majalisa mai kare hakkin dan Adam mai suna Peter Bone ya bayyana a wani zanga-zanga a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta "fita yanzu" idan Farage ne ya yi shawarwarin ficewa daga Birtaniya.
Kalubale da May ke fuskanta na hada kan jam'iyyar da ta rabu biyu ya bayyana ne a yayin da 'yan gurguzu suka halarci wani zanga-zangar nuna adawa da ficewar Birtaniya daga EU.
Firaministan kasar na gwagwarmayar ci gaba da shirin sulhunta tsakanin masu goyon bayan ficewa daga EU da masu goyon bayan ci gaba da ficewa daga EU.
Abokan hulɗar ta sun nace cewa duk da koma baya, za ta ci gaba da ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels , ta haka ne za ta tilasta wa masu shakkar Euro da Labour su zaɓi tsakanin kunshin ta ko 'hargitsi'.
A wani zanga-zangar Leave Means Leave da aka yi a Solihull, Bone ya sanar da cewa zai yi watsi da shirin Chequers.
Ya bayyana cewa ya kamata a hada Farage kuma a ba shi alhakin tattaunawar da Brussels.
Ya ce, "Idan shi ne ke da alhakin wannan, da mun fita yanzu".
