A gaban taron, abokin aikinmu na Labour, Lord Adonis, ya yi ba'a game da matsalolin tsaro da ake fuskanta a cikin manhajar jam'iyyar Conservative.
"Su ne mutanen da ke da'awar cewa suna da iko da tsarin IT da fasaha na Kanada, don kula da iyakoki, don cinikin kyauta ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland", in ji shi.
"Wannan abin dariya ne.
Ya ce, "Babu wani abu da ake kira Brexit mai kyau".
