Sabuntawa game da furen algae: Rage yawan ruwa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ta bayar ya nuna cewa yawan algae a yankunan da ke yankin Tampa Bay yana raguwa.
A cewar FWC, an bayar da rahoton cewa akwai wasu fure-fure a cikin yankin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier , wanda ke nuna cewa yawan ya ragu.
Wannan fure-fure na algae yana shimfidawa a cikin iyakar bakin teku na kilomita 210 daga arewacin Pinellas County zuwa kudancin Lee County.
Akwai wasu ƙananan furanni a cikin kilomita 10 daga bakin teku a gundumar Hillsborough, amma ba su da yawa kamar na makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da fure-fure a cikin Pasco County.
An bayar da rahoton matsakaici a cikin ko a cikin teku a cikin Pinellas County a cikin makon da ya gabata, ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a cikin teku a cikin Hillsborough County, babban taro a cikin Manatee County, babban taro a cikin ko a cikin teku a cikin Sarasota County, matsakaici a cikin Charlotte County, babban taro a cikin ko a cikin teku a cikin Lee County da ƙananan taro a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahoton rashin numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Babu wani rahoton rashin numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a cikin mako guda.
